
I began to walk to my bedroom. I've never felt so powerless in my life. Being constantly harassed by a demon...
I made sure my door was locked before I began to undress and change into my nightgown.
I crawled under the sheets and closed my eyes. Suddenly, something was sitting on the bed next to me.
"Sweet dreams, my love.~"
